Author: dpapathanasiou
Content:
A while ago, I remember reading on Emanuel Derman's blog (http://www.wilmott.com/blogs/eman/) a comment along the lines of "Time and the right to choose have value".

So while I'm sure you can find some job to pay the bills, consider how much time (and in what state mentally/physically) it will leave you to focus on your startup.\n

Author: whacked_new
Content: Interesting. If Mark sold to Yahoo, maybe none of this would have happened. By releasing the API, facebook also de-monopolizes its information. This perhaps lowers FB's pricetag per user. And perhaps Mark knows this.
